de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensor

Interface HeartRateSensor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractHeartRateSensor, AdidasHRM, PolarH7, TomTomHRM

    public interface HeartRateSensor
    This interface defines methods for interpreting and calculating heart rate data from the Bluetooth specification. The raw heart rate values as hexadecimal contains a configuration byte as prefix. Dependent on the bits set in this byte, the additional values are interpreted accordingly.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
